<p>Developed a comprehensive web application using <strong>Vue.js 3 (Composition API)</strong>, designed to optimize project and task management in digitalization workflows. The app delivers a responsive, real-time user experience powered by Firebase, enabling precise tracking of task progress, timing, and workload management.</p>
<p><strong>Key features and technologies:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Real-time data synchronization:</strong> Firebase Firestore and Realtime Database keep information consistent and up to date across users and devices.</li>
  <li><strong>Lexoffice API integration:</strong> Automates accounting workflows (invoice generation and financial synchronization) to reduce manual overhead and improve efficiency.</li>
  <li><strong>Advanced barcode generation and scanning:</strong> QuaggaJS automates item identification, improves data accuracy, and streamlines workflow processes.</li>
  <li><strong>Sophisticated state management:</strong> Vuex manages complex nested data structures, ensuring scalability and maintainability.</li>
  <li><strong>Asynchronous programming patterns:</strong> Vuex actions and mutations handle complex data fetching and updates efficiently.</li>
  <li><strong>Responsive and accessible UI:</strong> Delivers smooth functionality across desktop and mobile platforms.</li>
  <li><strong>Vue Router-based navigation:</strong> Provides intuitive user flows and efficient view transitions.</li>
  <li><strong>Comprehensive validation and error handling:</strong> Maintains data integrity and offers clear user feedback.</li>
  <li><strong>Continuous integration & deployment:</strong> Firebase Hosting with CI workflows supports ongoing development and rapid iteration.</li>
  <li><strong>Strong problem-solving & scalable data modeling:</strong> Recursive aggregation logic for accurate project time tracking.</li>
    <li>User authentication and role-based user management using Firebase Authentication to secure access and control permissions within the app.</li>
</ul>
<p>This project showcases the ability to deliver end-to-end, scalable frontend applications integrated with backend APIs and cloud services, emphasizing automation, real-time data handling, and user-centric design.</p>'
